        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Deschutes River Conservancy Reauthorization Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill (1) reauthorizes the Deschutes River Conservancy Working Group through FY2032, (2) increases from 5% to 10% the amount authorized to be provided to the working group, and (3) changes the composition of the members of the working group.</p>]]>
        </text>
